1:01:18.375 --> 1:01:20.707
Paris edition of the New York herald.

1:01:20.708 --> 1:01:22.869
Radium x claims third victim.

1:01:26.583 --> 1:01:29.780
Radium x claims third victim.

1:01:29.792 --> 1:01:32.158
Radium x claims third victim.

1:01:33.125 --> 1:01:35.787
Radium x claims third victim.

